name: Julian Londono
about: Productivity is a lifestyle: when I'm not working with my team on CU Reviews you'll find me working on Info Sci research, exploring curiosity-driven side projects, mountain biking, or playing soccer. I'm always trying to expand my technical knowledge and skill sets as well as explore more of the world whenever possible. Fun fact: I took a road-trip from New Jersey to California and back this past summer and it was a blast!
